Name: collective.behavior.size
Version: 0.3
Summary: Provides size related behavior, such as weight and three dimensional size, to dexterity content types.
Home-page: https://github.com/collective/collective.behavior.size/
Author: Taito Horiuchi
Author-email: taito.horiuchi@gmail.com
License: BSD
Description: ========================
        collective.behavior.size
        ========================
        
        collective.behavior.size provides size related behavior, such as weight and three dimensional size, to dexterity content types.
        
        Currently Tested with
        ---------------------
        
        * Plone-4.3.2 with Python-2.7.x [taito]
        
        Behavior
        --------
        
        The behavior can be added through the web or directly through the file system to the dexterity content type xml file like::
        
          <property name="behaviors">
            ...
            <element value="collective.behavior.size.interfaces.ISize" />
            ...
          </property>
        
